{"article_id":"pRyGCXPxD4AXXCX8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trump campaign foreign policy adviser George Papadopoulos was sentenced Friday to 14 days in federal prison","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"for lying to the FBI .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"|","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Jacquelyn Martin/AP Photo","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Papadopoulos :","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"I was 'pinned ' in FBI interview","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"George Papadopoulos , the former Trump campaign aide , said on Sunday","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that he felt \" pinned \" during his fateful interview with FBI officers in January 2017 ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and that he lied to investigators in an attempt to protect President Donald Trump .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"On Friday , Papadopoulos was sentenced to 14 days in federal prison","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"for making false statements to the FBI during the early days of the Justice Department ' s investigation into Russian meddling in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"On Sunday , he was interviewed on ABC ' s \" This Week . \"","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"\" At the time of my interview with the FBI ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"around three or four days before that ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"I was at the inauguration","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"attending parties with senior-level transition officials , \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Papadopoulos told George Stephanopoulos .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"\" I understood","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that there was an incipient investigation into Russian interference in the 2016 election . \"","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" And I found myself as somebody","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"who worked incredibly hard over the past year with the campaign","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to actually have the candidate Trump be elected , \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"\" And then I found myself pinned between the Department of Justice and the sitting president","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and having probing questions","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that I thought","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"might incriminate the sitting president . \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Various reports have indicated","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"that statements by Papadopoulos to an Australian official in May 2016 triggered the initial investigation into Russian interference in the election .","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"Playbook PM","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Sign up for our must-read newsletter on what 's driving the afternoon in Washington .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"By signing up","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Papadopoulos said on Sunday","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that he believed","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"he did not incriminate Trump in his 2017 talks with law enforcement .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"\" I didn ' t understand really the nature of what was going on , \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" Of course I ' m remorseful ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"I ' m contrite ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"and I did lie ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"but ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"you know ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"you ' re just taken off guard ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"I guess ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"in a such a momentous situation","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"where you ' re potentially sitting there ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"incriminating the president ,","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"even though of course I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"I did . \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"He added :","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"\" You know ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that was probably in the back of my mind ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"of what exactly am I doing here","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"talking about Russian hacking or election interference with the candidate","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that I just worked for . \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"The former foreign policy adviser pleaded guilty in October to lying to the FBI about his meetings in London with a Maltese professor , Joseph Mifsud","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"- making Papadopoulos the first person","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"to admit guilt to Robert Mueller in the special counsel ' s sprawling Russia inquiry .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"\" He basically presented himself as this well-connected , well-traveled former diplomat","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"who could essentially connect me and the campaign to Russian officials and to other leaders around the world , \"","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Papadopoulos said of Mifsud .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Mifsud told Papadopoulos in the spring of 2016","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that he had obtained \" dirt \" on Hillary Clinton ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and would claim to have amassed troves of emails","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"connected to Clinton ' s campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"according to Mueller ' s prosecutors .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" He sat me down","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and he was quite giddy , \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Papadopoulos said .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" And he told me ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"' I have information","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that the Russians have thousands of Hillary Clinton ' s emails . ' \"","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"A month before that meeting , the emails of Clinton ' s campaign chairman , John Podesta , were stolen in a data breach .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Mueller indicted 12 Russian intelligence officers in relation to the crime in July , as well as on charges of cyberattacks on the Democratic National Committee and other liberal targets .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Papadopoulos maintained","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that he was not made aware of the hacks on Podesta or the DNC ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and has testified","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"that he did not tell any Trump campaign officials about his conversation with Mifsud","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"regarding Clinton ' s emails .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Papadopoulos said","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"he chose to keep the professor ' s claim under wraps","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"because Paul Manafort","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"- shortly after becoming the Trump campaign chairman in May 2016 -","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"quashed the idea of a potential summit between then-candidate Donald Trump and President Vladimir Putin of Russia ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"which Papadopoulos had been trying to broker .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"\" As far as I remember ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"it didn ' t seem that Paul Manafort wanted to pursue this meeting , \"","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Papadopoulos said on Sunday .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" So","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"as far as I remember ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"why on Earth would I then ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"after I was shut down in a ,","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"I guess","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"in a formal way ,","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"after a lot of vacillating between the campaign ,","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"would I then tell the campaign something like that ? \"","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"Sen. Mark Warner of Virginia , the top Democrat on the Senate Intelligence Committee , said on Sunday","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"it was unlikely that Papadopoulos did not tell other members of the Trump campaign about his talks with Mifsud .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"\" One thing is fairly clear :","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"This is an ambitious guy","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"who wants to be a player in the Trump campaign , \"","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Warner said of Papadopoulos on CNN ' s \" State of the Union . \"","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"\" Trump had chosen him as part of his foreign policy team , \"","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Warner said .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"\" It just stretches ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"I think ,","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"most people ' s credibility","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"that ,","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"if Papadopoulos had this knowledge","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"and he wanted to try to further ingratiate himself with the campaign ,","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"that he wouldn ' t have shared that with somebody on the campaign . \"","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"Papadopoulos also said","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"he had \" no opinion on \" and \" no knowledge of \" Trump ' s alleged attempts","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"to obstruct Mueller ' s investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and could not answer","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"whether the special counsel would be able to demonstrate coordination between the Trump campaign and the Kremlin .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"\" I have no idea , \"","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"he said on Sunday .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"\" All","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"I can say","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"is that my testimony might have helped move something towards that ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"but I have no idea . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":133,"right":254,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":131,"right":132,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":129,"right":130,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"}